Andy Murray beats Viktor Troicki to reach Queen's Club final
Watch the five best points from Andy Murray's semi-finalvictory over Viktor Troickiat Queen's Club.The three-time champion won 6-3 7-6 (7-4) and will face South Africa's Kevin Anderson in the final.After rain had stopped play on Saturday evening, Murray required only 65 minutes on Sunday to complete the job against the Serb world number 25.